WEBVTT

00:01.502 --> 00:02.368
<i>SHORE: Previously</i>
<i>on "The Practice"...</i>

00:02.402 --> 00:04.003
Suddenly,
airport security comes

00:04.037 --> 00:05.639
and tells me
I have to get off

00:05.672 --> 00:07.908
because I was too fat to fly.

00:07.941 --> 00:09.175
ASHFORD: The statute
of limitations

00:09.209 --> 00:11.011
for suing us has expired.

00:11.044 --> 00:12.513
I would just tell the client
that we settled,

00:12.546 --> 00:13.714
pay them out
of my own pocket,

00:13.747 --> 00:16.248
and avoid the whole
malpractice thing.

00:16.282 --> 00:19.853
They've agreed
to pay you $10,000.

00:19.886 --> 00:21.187
Tell them no.

00:21.221 --> 00:22.689
FRUTT: This woman thinks
the airline

00:22.723 --> 00:24.725
offered her $10,000?

00:24.758 --> 00:25.859
Just help me.

00:25.892 --> 00:27.894
Tell your client the truth.

00:27.928 --> 00:29.395
There's something
you need to know.

00:29.429 --> 00:30.396
I already know.

00:30.764 --> 00:32.566
And all I can say
is thank you.

00:32.598 --> 00:34.835
Mr. Torrance came
to my house this morning.

00:34.868 --> 00:36.069
STRINGER:
He went to Melissa Kenner

00:36.102 --> 00:38.071
and pretended to be somebody
from the airline

00:38.104 --> 00:39.339
and settled the case.

00:39.372 --> 00:41.742
Well, any chance
I get to break a law.

00:42.843 --> 00:43.910
Why are we having lunch?

00:43.944 --> 00:45.946
SHORE: I think
I enjoy the company

00:45.979 --> 00:46.880
of inquisitive people.

00:46.913 --> 00:49.115
Also, I find you attractive.

00:49.149 --> 00:50.551
I was so sure

00:50.584 --> 00:52.252
after the case
was over that--

00:52.285 --> 00:53.720
SHORE:
That you were expendable?

00:53.954 --> 00:55.288
Just the opposite, Diane.

00:58.224 --> 00:59.259
It's not a Jewish thing.

00:59.292 --> 01:00.100
What is it, then?

01:00.133 --> 01:01.768
STRINGER: A man-woman thing.

01:01.802 --> 01:03.970
I want a break up.

01:04.004 --> 01:06.239
Jamie, you and I,
it's just a thing.

01:06.272 --> 01:08.675
We both know that.
It's no big deal.

01:15.015 --> 01:18.018
(music playing)

01:42.108 --> 01:43.476
What are you doing?

01:44.244 --> 01:45.779
Just looking.

01:46.947 --> 01:48.348
You're just looking?

01:50.817 --> 01:51.885
I leave.

01:56.356 --> 01:58.659
