on my part.

02:17.917 --> 02:19.352
To the contrary, um,

02:20.887 --> 02:23.957
but in the spirit of honesty--

02:24.691 --> 02:25.759
You leave?

02:29.195 --> 02:32.198
(indistinct chatter)

02:42.643 --> 02:44.244
WILSON: Okay,
you'll be transported

02:44.277 --> 02:46.747
