02:53.554 --> 02:54.655
as will I.

02:56.590 --> 02:59.225
You might want to think
about a plea.

02:59.259 --> 03:00.501
Aggravated rape

03:00.534 --> 03:02.368
could be as much as 25 years.

03:02.402 --> 03:04.004
Can I ask you something?

03:04.037 --> 03:05.471
Certainly.

03:05.506 --> 03:07.808
WILLS: How is it that I'm going
on trial tomorrow

03:07.841 --> 03:10.210
