after 8:00 P. M.

05:07.207 --> 05:09.610
I was picking up Jessica
to go out to dinner.

05:09.643 --> 05:11.778
It was her 21st birthday.

05:11.812 --> 05:13.814
Jessica is your daughter?

05:13.847 --> 05:14.681
SAMUEL: Yes.

05:14.948 --> 05:16.282
I came into the house,

05:16.316 --> 05:18.184
and I immediately heard noise

05:18.218 --> 05:19.720
coming from somewhere.

05:19.753 --> 05:21.354
What kind of noise, sir?

05:21.722 --> 05:24.925
Well, I really couldn't
identify it at first,

05:24.958 --> 05:27.628
but then I went into
the living room

05:27.661 --> 05:29.596
and, uh, I,

05:29.630 --> 05:32.332
