for the jury

05:46.813 --> 05:48.849
exactly what you saw?

05:49.349 --> 05:51.885
SAMUEL: Jessica
was on her back,

05:51.918 --> 05:52.853
on the floor.

05:54.588 --> 05:56.489
That man over there
was on top of her.

05:57.758 --> 05:59.492
